<a href="/questions/165998-hi-to-those-who-ve-already-read-the">Hi,
To those who&#39;ve already read the book: Can you read it without having read Harold Fry?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_165998'><a id="like_count_community_question_165998" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/165998?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">9 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F20800188-the-love-song-of-miss-queenie-hennessy">like</a></span>

